<h3> See homepage for <!WA1><a href="http://www.cs.uiowa.edu/~cremer/scenario96.html"> Workshop on Scenario and Traffic Generation for Driving Simulation</a>, December 6-7, 1996. </h3> <P>

<h3> See homepage for <!WA2><a href="http://www.cs.uiowa.edu/~cremer/sive95.html"> The First Workshop on Simulation and Interaction in 
Virtual Environments </a>, July 13-15, 1995. </h3> <P>

<B> Research interests</B>; simulation, virtual environments, integration of numeric
and symbolic computing, geometric modeling, problem solving environments.

